comments: Anunoby (TOR) firms up in a legal screening position in Ingram's (NOP) path.
Ibaka (TOR) makes marginal contact with Melli (NOP) off ball.
Redick (NOP) contests Lowry's (TOR) jump shot attempt and gives him room to land safely.
VanVleet (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position on Ingram (NOP) and absorbs the contact at the end of the drive.
VanVleet (TOR) is late to establish himself in a legal guarding position when he delivers contact by turning his body into Ingram (NOP) and affecting his SQBR.
Gasol (TOR) places a forearm to Ingram (NOP) and does not affect his SQBR.
Siakam (TOR) dislodges Redick (NOP) from his legal guarding position.
Powell (TOR) rests his hand on Redick's (NOP) back but doesn't affect his SQBR.
Ingram (NOP) establishes himself in a screening position in Anunoby's (TOR) path and absorbs the contact.
VanVleet (TOR) cleanly dislodges the ball from Hart (NOP) during his drive.
Melli (NOP) establishes himself in Anunoby's (TOR) path when he absorbs the contact on the screen.
Hart (NOP) makes contact to Lowry's (TOR) body during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Melli (NOP) establishes himself in a screening position in Anunoby's (TOR) path and absorbs the contact.
Melli (NOP) firms up in a screening position in Lowry's (TOR) path when they make marginal upper leg to leg contact.
Anunoby (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Holiday (NOP).
Gasol (TOR) pulls Melli's (NOP) jersey away from his body during the shot attempt.
Gasol (TOR) is established in Jackson's (NOP) path before the contact during the screen.
Jackson (NOP) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Powell (TOR).
Powell (TOR) makes marginal contact with Ingram (NOP) in the post and does not affect his SQBR.
Ingram (NOP) cleanly dislodges the ball from Powell (TOR) on the rebound.
Melli (NOP) and Anunoby (TOR) engage and disengage on the rebound.
VanVleet (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in Melli's path.
Holiday (NOP) lands in front of Lowry (TOR) and the contact is created by Lowry extending his leg during the follow-through on his jump shot.
Powell (TOR) briefly places his hand on Holiday's (NOP) opposite side hip but quickly slides it off, and the contact does not affect his FOM.
Melli (NOP) does not step out of bounds when he receives the pass before taking the jump shot.
Holiday (NOP) moves laterally into Lowry's (TOR) path and the contact affects his SQBR.
Hart (NOP) jumps vertically and is turned during the contact initiated by VanVleet (TOR) on his driving shot attempt.
Gasol (TOR) makes leg to leg contact with Hart (NOP) that affects his SQBR.
Melli (NOP) establishes himself in a legal screening position and absorbs the contact from Anunoby (TOR).
Redick (NOP) steps out of bounds as he receives the pass.
